nodes.title: Image Background (Left)
widgets_values:
Background:** The scene is set against a high-contrast black-and-white image of a Japanese woman athlete in deep focus during a training session. The stark monochrome palette emphasizes the elite nature of her endeavor, with sharp lines that suggest precision and dedication.

**Foreground:** The athlete, dressed in sleek black leggings and a white tank top that suggests modesty while highlighting her toned physique, leaps gracefully, embodying strength and agility. Her footwear is minimalist yet functional white trainers with black accents. She looks directly at the viewer with a calm, confident smile.
